## Task 3 WHOIS

- WHOIS provides domain registration info.
- Registrants can set DNS records.
- WHOIS records include: domain name, registrar, creation/expiration dates, registrant details.
- Privacy services can mask personal info.
Example:
- Code
whois example.com
Registrar: GoDaddy.com
Creation Date: 1993-04-02
Expiration Date: 2026-10-20
Registrant: Registration Private (Domains By Proxy)

